title: Priya and Her Mom's Cheesy Tomato Rice | Cook #WithMe | NYT Cooking
description:
Get the recipe: https://nyti.ms/2Ww9rdS

Priya Krishna in the house! Her parents’ house, that is, and she’s joined by her mom, Ritu Krishna. The mother-daughter duo are making Tomato Rice With Crispy Cheddar (think: pizza in rice form) from their "Indian-ish" cookbook,  while Priya’s dad, Shailendra, flexes some serious camera skills.
